\mt1 Preface  
\ip This publication is the New Testament in the N…ôfe lan…°ua…°e. The 3000 speakers of N…ôfe live in Southeast Tanna, which is located in TAFEA province in southern Vanuatu.  
\ip The New Testament in the N…ôfe lan…°ua…°e was translated durin…° the years 2003 to 2013 by the South Tanna Translation and Literacy Project.  
\is1 N…ô…°kiariien s…ô rakupw…ôn  
\is1 In i n…ô…°kiariien s…ôv…ôi translesen r…®nostat mo wok ir…ô meste ro sampam  
\ip Fwe kupw…ôn aposol me s…ôv…ôi Iesu Kristo m…®ne n…ôrmama me nepw…®n ipaka t…® nir…ôha h…ôm…ôrai n…ôkuku…ô me s…ôv…ôi Niutestamen. Ir…ôha h…ôm…ôrai n…ôkuku…ô me n…ôha ia n…ô…°kiariien i Krik. Ro iam…®nhi ir…ô t…® n…ôri n…ô m…ô n…ô…°kiariien s…ôv…ôi n…ôkur Kris r…ômwhen ia kampani n…ô…°kiariien ia kwopun n…ôha Metel Ist fwe kupw…ôn. Fwe kupw…ôn n…ôrmama me ia Metel Ist n…ô…°kiariien me s…ôv…ônraha h…ôn…ôtui pehe ir…ô s…ôp…ôms…ôp…ô, m…ôt…ô ko krai n…ôkuku…ô riti ia n…ô…°kiariien i Krik ir…ôha pam h…ôvsini mh…ôukur…ôn n…®pwran t…® n…ôri n…ô m…ô in n…ô kampani n…ô…°kiariien s…ôv…ônraha. Ipwet m…®ne ko ik…ôvsini n…ô…°kiariien i Krik ik…ôt…ô m…ô ro iam…®nhi ir…ô m…®ne: ·ºòŒΩ ·ºÄœÅœá·øá ·º¶ŒΩ ·ΩÅ Œª·ΩπŒ≥ŒøœÇ, Œ∫Œ±·Ω∂ ·ΩÅ Œª·ΩπŒ≥ŒøœÇ ·º¶ŒΩ œÄœÅ·Ω∏œÇ œÑ·Ω∏ŒΩ Œ∏Œµ·ΩπŒΩ, Œ∫Œ±·Ω∂ Œ∏Œµ·Ω∏œÇ ·º¶ŒΩ ·ΩÅ Œª·ΩπŒ≥ŒøœÇ. (Jon 1:1)  
\ip Kuv…ôrai raka Niutestamen fwe kupw…ôn ia n…ô…°kiariien Krik, kurir…ô ir…ô n…ô…°kiariien amasan s…ôv…ôi Iesu Kristo ruvir…®s mev…ôn mwi meste nari fwe kwopun me nepw…®n n…ôrmama h…ôreirei n…ô…°kiariien Krik ik…®n. Ro iam…®nhi ir…ô n…ôrmama me ia kwopun me n…ôha h…ônam…ômwur m…ônamh…ôuvsini n…ô…°kiariien Krik ia Niutestamen ruvehe ia n…ô…°kiariien me s…ôv…ônraha s…ôp…ôms…ôp…ô.  
\ip Ia nuk 2001 n…ôkur ia T…ôn…ô s…ôm…ôme kamh…ôni n…ô…°kiariien i N…ôfe h…ômter ia kusen riti s…ôv…ônraha s…ôv…ôi nuvsiniien n…ô…°kiariien ruvehe ia N…ôfe. Kani n…ô…°hi kusen n…ôha m…ô Saot Tana Translesen mo Litresi Projek. Kurir…ô ir…ô n…ôrmama ia kusen n…ôha h…ôrhi pen n…ôresien riti rev…ôn t…® Vanuatu Baebol Translesen (VBT) fwe ia Vila. N…ôrmama ia kusen s…ôv…ôi nuvsiniien n…ô…°kiariien ruvehe ia N…ôfe r…ôres VBT m…ô tr…ôtui ro i…ôrmama riti truvehe masitu ia nir…ôha t…® noien wok. I…ôrmama s…ô trasitu iam…®nha ir…ô kani wok s…ôv…ônhi m…ô in r…ômwhen ia advaesa. Ia 2003 VBT r…ôrhi pen advaesa riti rev…ôn mar…ô te…°…®n n…ôrmama fwe ia rukw…ônu n…ôha Ienmarei. N…ôp…®n advaesa n…ôha ruv…ôuvehe raka, n…ôn…ô rukw…ônu me m…®ne nimw…ôfwaki me fwe Irupou meste nari fwe Krinpoen h…ôrhi pen n…ôrmama me s…ôv…ônraha h…ôuv…ôn k…ôru k…ôru mhous…ôs…®mw…®n ir…ôha me ia Kwamera. Ia n…ôkureien n…ôha s…ôv…ônraha, ir…ôha h…ôrpwi r…ô…°…®nraha ia nir…ôha me nepw…®n m…ô tuhamowok ipaka t…® advaesa, mamh…ôuvsini n…ô…°kiariien ia Niutestamen ruvehe ia n…ô…°kiariien i N…ôfe. Ia nuk 2004 kusen s…ôv…ôi nuvsiniien n…ô…°kiariien ruvehe ia N…ôfe roeite mwi n…ôrmama me ham…ôuku pen ia rukw…ônu me m…®ne nimw…ôfwaki me pam. N…ôrmama me n…ôha h…ôuvehe mh…ôseni noien tukrai n…ô…°kiariien N…ôfe ir…ô. Ro iam…®nhi ir…ô kusen s…ôv…ôi nuvsiniien n…ô…°kiariien ruvehe ia N…ôfe r…®namo vi wok s…ôv…ônhi ia nuk 2004, m…ôrki meste mo sampam ia Niutestamen ia nuk 2013. Ia nuk 2013 kusen s…ôv…ôi nuvsiniien n…ô…°kiariien ruvehe ia N…ôfe roeite mwi n…ôrmama ia rukw…ônu me m…®ne nimw…ôfwaki me pam h…ôuvehe k…ôvsini irapw Niutestamen ir…ôha pam h…ôre…°i fwe Matiu meste Revelesen. N…ôp…®n h…ôuv…ôre…°i pam h…ôseni m…ô ramasan pam.  
\is1 Suatuk s…ô transleta me h…ônesi pen t…® nuvsiniien n…ô…°kiariien ia Niutestamen ruvehe ia n…ô…°kiariien i N…ôfe  
\ip N…ô…°kiariien i Krik k…®m…ôrai Niutestamen ir…ô fwe kupw…ôn rop…ô ia n…ô…°kiariien i N…ôfe n…ôrmama ia Saot Tana kamh…ôni ipwet m…®ne. Ko transleta me h…ôuvsini n…ô…°kiariien Krik ruvehe ia n…ô…°kiariien i N…ôfe resi pen noien s…ôv…ôi n…ô…°kiariien n…ôkur Kris kamh…ôni fwe kupw…ôn, m…ôt…ô saon s…ôv…ônhi tr…®pkatukwatukw mh…ô. Ro iam…®nhi ir…ô, n…ôp…®n transleta me ho p…ôri wok ir…ôha advaesa, ir…ôha h…ômwur m…ô (1) translesen s…ôv…ônraha tr…®ni irapw n…®pwrai n…ô…°kiariien s…ôv…ôi n…ô…°kiariien Krik, n…ôn…ô (2) translesen s…ôv…ônraha tresi pen atukwatukw n…ô…°kiariien i N…ôfe m…®ne suatuk s…ô n…ôrmama kamh…ôni n…ô…°kiariien i N…ôfe ipwet m…®ne. N…ôp…®n transleta me ho p…ôri wok ir…ôha advaesa, ir…ôha h…ôti pen p…®k ia Niutestamen k…®m…ôrai ia n…ô…°kiariien Krik kupw…ôn. M…ôt…ô h…ôti pen mwi ia translesen me nepw…®n. Translesen me n…ôha h…ôti pen p…®k ia nir…ôha ir…ôha i Revised Standard Version (RSV), Good News Bible (GNB), m…®ne Bislama (BSL).  
\is1 N…ô…°kiariien mi n…ôha kani irau m…ô futnot m…®ne refrens  
\ip Tik…ôvsini Niutestamen i ia n…ô…°kiariien i N…ôfe, m…ôtoni ia kwopun me nepw…®n leta riti k…®m…ôrai ram…ômak ut…ô ia nusvenhi n…ô…°kiariien riti. Tik…ôtoni m…ô ro iam…®nhi ir…ô (\f + \fr 1:0 \ft Hemia nao wan futnot.\f*). Leta n…ôha ramahat…ôn pen m…ô n…ô…°kiariien riti ram…ômak inh…ôr…®pw anan ia n…®mwai n…ôkuku…ô n…ôha ikam…ôvsini. Tik…ôvsini n…ô…°kiariien n…ôha inh…ôr…®pw anan ramahat…ôn n…®pwrai n…ô…°kiariien riti u…ô suatuk riti mwi t…® nuvsiniien n…ô…°kiariien n…ôha ruvehe ia N…ôfe. Kani n…ô…°kiariien s…ô ro iam…®nha ir…ô m…ô futnot.  
\ip Kwopun k…®m…ôrai pen futnot me ik…®n ia n…®mwai n…ôkuku…ô tik…ôtoni mwi inh…ôr…®pw ir…ô n…ô…°kiariien me nepw…®n kamh…ôni vas me nepw…®n mwi ia N…ôkuku…ô Ikinan. Kani vas me n…ôha m…ô refrens. Tik…ôvsini refrens me n…ôha trahat…ôn vas me nepw…®n mwi ia N…ôkuku…ô Ikinan kamh…ô…°kiari ia nari riti r…ômwhen ia vas n…ôha k…®no mak ir…ô ram…ô…°kiari mwi ir…ô.  
\is1 N…ôn…®mwi nari me  
\ip Tik…ôvsini pam Niutestamen i ia n…ô…°kiariien i N…ôfe, mar…ô m…ôtoni mwi n…®p…ôri n…ôkuku…ô riti mwi n…ôha ik…®n n…ôn…®mwi nari me h…ôp…®k ir…ô. N…ôn…®mwi nari me n…ôha trasitu ia niram m…ô tikukur…ôn amasan mwi narimnari me nepw…®n N…ôkuku…ô Ikinan ram…ô…°kiari ir…ô m…ôt…ô nepw…®n riw…ôn ia Vanuatu. Tik…ôti pen ia n…ôn…®mwi nari me n…ôha m…ôtoni narimnari me r…ômwhen ia nei me, u…ô n…ôrim…®ru me, u…ô narimnari me nepw…®n s…ôv…ôi nar…ôien i n…ôkur Isrel m…®ne n…ôkur Rom h…ônar…ô ir…ô fwe kupw…ôn m…ôt…ô riw…ôn ia Vanuatu.  
\is1 Map me  
\ip Tik…ôvsini Niutestamen i ia n…ô…°kiariien i N…ôfe, m…ôtoni map me nepw…®n. Ia map me n…ôha tik…ôtoni kwopun me nepw…®n Iesu ramav…ôn ik…®n fwe kupw…ôn. Map me nepw…®n mwi kamhahat…ôn nav…ônien me s…ôv…ôi Pol n…ôp…®n in ramav…ôn ir…ô mamev…ôn ia kwopun me mam…ôvisau irapw n…ô…°kiariien amasan s…ôv…ôi Iesu Kristo.  
\is1 N…ôkuku…ô s…ô rani irapw n…®pwrai n…ô…°kiariien me (Diksonari)  
\ip Tr…®ni m…®nu…ô ik…ôtoni n…ô…°kiariien riti ia Niutestamen s…ô ikreirei n…®pwran ramasan m…ô tik…ômwur m…ôtoni m…ô k…®m…ôrai pen n…ô…°kiariien n…ôha ia diksonari u…ô rek…ôm. Diksonari n…ôha in n…®p…ôri n…ôkuku…ô sampam, mam…®ni irapw n…®pwrai n…ô…°kiariien me nepw…®n.  
\is1 N…®pwrai n…®niien me  
\ip Tr…®ni m…®nu…ô ikokeikei m…ô tikahat…ôn n…ôrmama ia nari riti s…ô N…ôkuku…ô Ikinan ram…ô…°kiari ir…ô, ramasan m…ô tik…ôtoni n…®p…ôri n…ôkuku…ô s…ô rani n…®pwrai n…®niien me.  